premise_source_doc_sentence: Melanie Deanne Paxson  (  née Moore ; born September 26 , 1972  )  is an American actress .
She is known for her roles as Jaclyn in Cupid , Sara Brennan in Happy Family and as Julie in Notes from the Underbelly .
Paxson also appeared in a number of Gladware television commercials in the early 2000s .
